name: 2D Castle Interior Objects
description:
Easy to modify and use, great for fantasy games, here is your shot!

Carefully labelled and layered 7 PSD files, including the sample scene.

Doors, windows, tiles, stones.... over 40 items are ready to be used!

Enjoy this hand-painted, pixel based, unique 2D castle interior set.

PREVIEW: https://imgur.com/a/0PEV3sR

* 7 transparent PNG's

* 6 PSD files, including the demo scene.

* More than 40 fantasy objects
